title: Miley Cyrus, Flaming Lips planning `completely naked show` with milk
text:
*Washington D.C., Oct. 14 (ANI): Miley Cyrus and American rock band The Flaming Lips are planning a nude concert for a music video.*
Washington D.C., Oct. 14 (ANI): Miley Cyrus and American rock band The Flaming Lips are planning a nude concert for a music video. Lead singer Wayne Coyne posted a picture on Instagram of a naked split-shot of the band and Cyrus, captioning "Oh f--k..!!! @mileycyrus is planning a show where her, the band (us) and the audience are all COMPLETELY naked with milk (well white stuff that looks like milk) is being spewed everywhere.. It's a video (in the works) for #mileycyrusandherdeadpetz song 'The Milky Milky Milk'..," E!Online reports Earlier, the 22-year-old singer revealed that she would be touring with The Flaming Lips in support of her surprise album 'Miley Cyrus and Her Dead Petz.'
